transcript:
Executive: Haan abhi aur koi issue nahi hai na apna?
Customer: Nahi abhi nahi hai. Thoda sa dekho wo keyword wagera sahi customer ke hisab se wo hai ki nahi wo.
Executive: Keyword wagera sir sare mention hai aur main dekh hi rahi thi aur sare jo bache honge main sare add kar lungi usme koi issue nahi hai. 
Executive: Theek hai? Aur baki sir maine aapko bola hai ki aap mere personal number pe call kar lijiye.
Customer: Theek hai sir. Yaha pe kya hai na sir bar bar aap 9696 pe call karoge to bar bar concern raise hota hai.
Customer: Aapka number ek minute ruko.
Executive: Maine diya tha aapko.
Executive: Fir se le lo aap.
Customer: Nahi nahi theek hai ye wala na 661 last hai na.
Executive: Haan isi pe call kiya karo. Theek hai? Main aaj yaha se concern close kar rahi hu.
Customer: Haan theek hai.
